@NODE Rate "Please rate"
@KEYWORDS "Aminet, rate, charts"

Please rate
-----------

Please rate the Installer tools. To do so, send an email to aminet-server\@wuarchive.wustl.edu with the following content:

RATE util/misc/InstallerTools.lha <num>

where <num> is a mark from 0..10 with 10 being the best.
You can rate several programs in one mail.

Thank you!

@next Index
@ENDNODE

